    <h2>
      Activities
    </h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Check that there is a qualititative difference between <i>&#945;</i> = 
        0.5 and <i>&#945;</i> = 1.
      </li>
      <li>
        Find the boundary between these two different behaviors.
      </li>
      <li>
        Can you find other cases in which the collision is also elastic from 
        the &quot;macroscopic&quot; point of view?
      </li>
      <li>
        Which is the most inelastic case?
      </li>
    </ul>
